    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This upgrade does not use a room slot when purchased, and expires at the end of every month. It represents the party choosing to forego improvements to their living space and instead exchanging their IP for a temporary cost of living reduction.</p><p>Each time this upgrade is purchased, it reduces the cost of next month's rent by 1 Eagle/200eb, to a maximum of 1/2 the cost of rent. Once a month's rent has been paid, all instances of this upgrade immediately expire and must be purchased again.</p>"
